bleaching events.

00:15:19.670 --> 00:15:22.290
Sometimes they
recover, and the reef

00:15:22.290 --> 00:15:24.170
is getting back to its states.

00:15:24.170 --> 00:15:25.380
And sometimes it's too hard.

00:15:25.380 --> 00:15:27.400
