00:15:27.400 --> 00:15:30.000
So this will not disappear.

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:31.260
But the reef will change--

00:15:31.260 --> 00:15:32.820
how they will change?

00:15:32.820 --> 00:15:33.930
The system will change.

00:15:33.930 --> 00:15:36.450
The species will
adapt and change.

00:15:36.450 --> 00:15:39.220
How it will change, what will be
the fate of this in the future,

00:15:39.220 --> 00:15:39.900
we don't know.

